column5: Year in School (Must be a Junior or Senior)
column14: Why do you think this nominee will make a positive impact as a Lincoln G.O.L.D. member?
column15: List of 2 References to Include: Name, Phone, and Email

column14: Rachel is an outgoing, smart and charming leader. She makes a positive impact in every program she gets involved in. She is a top student and is involved in the chorus program at Pius. In addition she has been a leader in Girl Scouts, dance, chorus and in her youth group at church. As the daughter of a career Naval officer, she has moved frequently and has been exposed to many different cities, leaders and schools. Her background and experience would bring new thoughts and a wide perspective to the table.
